{"id":625469,"title":"99｜理论盘点：Web 客户端与服务端","content":"<p><strong>课后习题</strong><br>\n请你使用 http.server 模块，将目录 /tmp 通过 HTTP 协议发布到 8080 端口，并通过浏览器验证是否发布成功。</p><p><strong>课程代码、课件及其他相关资料地址</strong><br>\n<a href=\"https://gitee.com/wilsonyin/zero-basics-python\">https://gitee.com/wilsonyin/zero-basics-python</a></p>","comments":[{"had_liked":false,"id":372045,"user_name":"涛哥","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":2748504,"ip_address":"上海","ucode":"D7C2DBF6291ACA","user_header":"","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1680650873,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100310001,"comment_content":"python3 -m http.server 8080 -d d:\\tmp","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":367985,"user_name":"繁星不灭","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":3042945,"ip_address":"广东","ucode":"7610E71D8FF224","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/2e/6e/81/a52fe3f6.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1675783075,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100310001,"comment_content":"一.习题练习\n1.执行命令\n#linux——IP：10.100.36.29\n[worker@python01 ~]$ python3 -m http.server 8080 -d &#47;tmp\n\n二.验证\n浏览器访问http:&#47;&#47;10.100.36.29:8080","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":367410,"user_name":"Cy23","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1591293,"ip_address":"辽宁","ucode":"8DC561C5151758","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/18/47/fd/895f0c27.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1675219197,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100310001,"comment_content":"python -m http.server -b 127.0.0.1 8080 -d .&#47;tmp","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":385249,"user_name":"Geek_631607","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":3789991,"ip_address":"广东","ucode":"EAF874838F0BE4","user_header":"","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1702350290,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100310001,"comment_content":"你可以使用 Python 的 `http.server` 模块来创建一个简单的 HTTP 服务器。以下是一个示例代码：\n\n```python\n# 导入必要的库\nimport http.server\nimport socketserver\n\n# 定义服务器的端口\nPORT = 8080\n\n# 更改工作目录到 &#39;&#47;tmp&#39;\nimport os\nos.chdir(&#39;&#47;tmp&#39;)\n\n# 创建一个请求处理器\nHandler = http.server.SimpleHTTPRequestHandler\n\n# 创建一个服务器\nwith socketserver.TCPServer((&quot;&quot;, PORT), Handler) as httpd:\n    print(f&quot;服务已启动，端口： {PORT}&quot;)\n    httpd.serve_forever()\n```\n\n这段代码会在 8080 端口上启动一个 HTTP 服务器，并将 &#39;&#47;tmp&#39; 目录发布到这个服务器上。你可以通过在浏览器中输入 `http:&#47;&#47;localhost:8080` 来访问这个服务器。\n\n**注意**：这段代码需要在你的本地环境中运行，而且你需要有足够的权限来访问 &#39;&#47;tmp&#39; 目录和开放 8080 端口。此外，`httpd.serve_forever()` 会让服务器一直运行，直到你手动停止它。如果你想在代码中自动停止服务器，你需要使用其他的方法，比如设置一个定时器。\n\n**安全提示**：在公共网络上发布你的文件可能会有安全风险，因为其他人可能会访问到你的文件。在你开始之前，确保你了解所有的风险，并采取适当的安全措施。如果你不确定，你应该咨询一个 IT 安全专家。希望这个答案对你有所帮助！","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":368014,"user_name":"Matthew","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":2843865,"ip_address":"江苏","ucode":"96093089773740","user_header":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/PiajxSqBRaEKSVuNarJuDhBSvHY0giaq6yriceEBKiaKuc04wCYWOuso50noqDexaPJJibJN7PHwvcQppnzsDia1icZkw/132","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1675820955,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100310001,"comment_content":"python3 -m http.server -b 127.0.0.1 8080 -d &#47;tmp","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1938853,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1d/95/a5/de5df896.jpg","nickname":"JSJohnsonJS","note":"","ucode":"732F8EA6078302","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":636364,"discussion_content":"python -m http.server -b 127.0.0.1 8080 -d ./tmp，必须要./表示当前目录，否则就是绝对目录了","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"